RichTextEditorIframeTitle.comment: {NeedsReview}[Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Title for the iframe in webpart RTE which will be read out by screen reader when editable field gains focus. {0} is the aria label passed to WebPartRTE. {1} is the general instructions of how to navigate to the formatting bar.

ToolbarNavigationTabKeys.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader instruction for using the tab key to switch toolbars.

ToolbarNavigationShiftTabKey.comment: {NeedsReview}[Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader instruction for using the shift + tab key to move the focus back to the textbox. It's only used in webpart RTE.
